casebody.data:
BAKER
v.
SHANAHAN 2018-0984 Supreme Court of Ohio. September 26, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur. O'Donnell, J., dissents and would deny respondent's motion to dismiss and grant an alternative writ. Fischer, J., not participating.
